{"type": "article", "id": 9606, "title": "龟壳背包", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-15T07:10:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702171828wixtao2BfhHE4SMA.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t来自旧金山的设计师 William Root 设计了一款特殊的背包，他的设计灵感来自乌龟极具保护性的外壳。他把书包做成了一个“壳”的模样，其中靠近身体的一面采用柔软的面料，而另一面则采用坚硬的做成多边形状的外壳，可以有效保护书包内的物件，同时具有防水功能。书包背面装有一个线状的灯，可以在黑夜里面保护使用者的安全，同时看起来也很酷。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171823TsgoDwhyQ7UJvlex.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.72666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021718247rbfMN5QjKOlzt3S.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171824k7UC3LsqdhOVSuXn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.72666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171825mchglQiJTp6WFC5U.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.72666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171825nvK3sj7wx5oYFUXe.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.72666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171826ROZcSrofwY9EHPCn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.72666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171826WQYEaoTGzFwj2mgv.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}